com.b2international.snowowl.core.api

Interface ExtendedComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IComponent<String>, IconIdProvider<String>, IdProvider<String>, LabelProvider, Serializable, TerminologyComponentIdProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtendedComponentImpl

    public interface ExtendedComponent
extends IComponent<String>, IconIdProvider<String>, TerminologyComponentIdProvider, Serializable
    Serializable representation of an extended component. Beside all component properties the additional properties are also available:

    • Returns with the icon ID of the component.
    • Returns with the terminology component ID.

    Implementations are restricted to use String as the unique component ID.

    See Also:
    IComponent, LabelProvider, TerminologyComponentIdProvider, IconIdProvider
